      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REDBRICK ASP (3) comes here following a sharp fourth over 275m at this track in 17.22. Should be in this for a long way. VINEGARHILL CASH (5) has been in the money at his last two runs, most recently when second beaten a head (17.18). Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Will give a great sight again. REAL GONE KID (4) broke a string of placings finishing in the money five on end before a last start fifth (17.72) at this track. Form here sound including 13 wins. Can figure in the finish. BALLYMAC BRETT (1) is in winning form and worth including in the main hopes.",
